  "text": "In addition to the feedback repression of the ilv-leu operon through CodY, we investigated the negative transcriptional regulation of the ilv-leu operon through another global regulator of nitrogen metabolism (TnrA) [CITATION_1] , initially inferred from DNA microarray data, obtained from analysis of the transcriptomes of the wild type and a tnrA disruptant [CITATION_2] .",
